# Environment Variables for Local GPT

# OpenAI API Key (Optional - for cloud AI fallback when Ollama is not available)
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# Note: 
# - If you don't set this, the app will work in demo mode when Ollama is not running
# - If you set this, the app will use OpenAI GPT when Ollama is not available
# - Local Ollama will always be preferred when available
